      short: "Professional endorsement of [RECIPIENT_NAME]. Their mastery of [SITUATION_STRENGTH] is evident in our [SITUATION_RELATIONSHIP] and their conduct has always been exemplary. I recommend them highly for any new opportunity that requires strategic thinking and dedication.",
      detailed: "[DATE]\n\n[RECIPIENT_NAME]\nPROFESSIONAL ENDORSEMENT AND REFERENCE\n\nTo whom it may concern,\n\nI am reaching out to provide a formal endorsement of [RECIPIENT_NAME]. In my capacity as [SENDER_TITLE], I [SITUATION_RELATIONSHIP] and have witnessed their dedication and mastery of [SITUATION_STRENGTH] across multiple key initiatives. They have a proven track record of delivering high-quality results under pressure and are a true asset to any professional environment.\n\nBeyond their technical skills, [RECIPIENT_NAME] is a quick learner and a strong collaborator who integrates seamlessly into various team structures. Their approach to professional challenges is always grounded in clear logic and foresight, ensuring that projects remain on track and exceed expectations. I have observed their growth first-hand and am confident in their ability to lead and contribute at the highest level. I recommend them highly for any new opportunity.\n\nThank you for your time in reviewing this professional endorsement. I look forward to hearing about [RECIPIENT_NAME]'s continued success in their future endeavors. Please contact me for any further information.",
