      short: "Recommend [RECIPIENT_NAME] for their dedication to [SITUATION_STRENGTH]. We [SITUATION_RELATIONSHIP] for several projects successfully over the years. They are a reliable and highly capable professional who consistently delivers results that exceed expectations.",
