      detailed: "[DATE]\n\nSCHOLARSHIP SELECTION COMMITTEE\n[COMPANY_NAME]\n\nSUBJECT: APPLICATION FOR THE [SCHOLARSHIP_NAME]\n\nTo the Scholarship Committee,\n\nI am submitting this letter to formally apply for the [SCHOLARSHIP_NAME]. Pursuing a degree in [SITUATION_FIELDOFSTUDY] has long been my primary academic and professional goal. This scholarship represents a vital opportunity for me to achieve these aspirations while contributing meaningfully to the field.\n\nMy interest in [SITUATION_FIELDOFSTUDY] began during my early education and has only intensified through my recent academic pursuits. With the support of this scholarship, I will be able to [SITUATION_IMPACT]. This financial assistance will allow me to focus entirely on my research and coursework, ensuring that I can reach my full potential as a scholar.\n\nI am a highly motivated student with a history of academic achievement and community involvement. I am confident that my dedication and passion for [SITUATION_FIELDOFSTUDY] make me an ideal candidate for this award. Thank you for your time and consideration of my application.",
      emailSubject: "Scholarship Application: [SENDER_NAME] - [SITUATION_FIELDOFSTUDY]",
      emailBody: "Dear Scholarship Committee,\n\nI am writing to formally submit my application for the [SCHOLARSHIP_NAME] to support my upcoming studies in [SITUATION_FIELDOFSTUDY]. Pursuing higher education in this field has always been a primary goal for me, and I am dedicated to achieving academic excellence.\n\nReceiving this scholarship would be a transformative opportunity, as it would enable me to [SITUATION_IMPACT] and focus entirely on my research and coursework. I have attached all the required documentation, including my academic transcripts and personal statement, for your review.\n\nThank you for your time and for considering my application. I look forward to the possibility of discussing my background and aspirations with the committee."
